==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea king
<hw>Sea" king`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>One of the leaders among the
Norsemen who passed their lives in roving the seas in search of plunder
and adventures; a Norse pirate chief. See the Note under
<er>Viking</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seal</ent>⟦br⟧
